## Research Sweep (run every 10 minutes max while active, rotate topics)

- **Cadence rule**: never remain idle/waiting more than 10 minutes if pending Nexus work, monitoring, or research checks to run.
- If no high-value action exists, perform a lightweight check (alerts/dependency/releases) before returning quiet status.

